      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require research facilities that use companion dogs, cats, or rabbits for research purposes and receive funding from the National Institutes of Health to offer such animals for adoption after completion of such research, and for other purposes.</title>
